  }, "\u2015 Orson Scott Card, Ender\u2019s Game")), mdx("p", null, "Should we not set any goals and just drift along? No! Even aforementioned buddhists faced this dilemma: if you are not supposed to desire anything in order to reach nirvana, why would you desire to reach nirvana in the first place?\nAnd the simplified answer is: just don\u2019t set ", mdx("em", {
