  }, "Mindfulness"), mdx("p", null, "Now, let\u2019s talk about better way of changing the story you\u2019re currently living in. Have you ever heard something like \u201Cfix your mind and Universe will rush to help\nyou in all your endeavors\u201D? Assuming that entire Universe would care about your endeavors is not only somewhat arrogant, it at the very least requires assumption that Universe can have \u201Cfeelings\u201D. If you are religious - you\u2019ve got both of those problems solved. What about the rest of us? Can Universe care? Remember how hard it\nwas to change spin direction (model you run in your head) in the \u201Cspinning dancer\u201D illusion from previous post? Now take a look at"), mdx("p", null, mdx("img", _extends({
    parentName: "p"
